  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "chapterTitle": "第一章 | 战役综述",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "23606318_3_693-827",
          "range": "693-827",
          "rangeStart": 693,
          "rangeEnd": 827,
          "markText": "民国二十六年八月四日￼，我奉委员长电召飞抵南京，委我任副参谋总长职。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1722484022,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-08-01 11:47:02",
          "chapterUid": 3,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23606318&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=693&rangeEnd=827",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2e32e507168342ef2e3766?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=693&rangeEnd=827"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23606318_3_1469-1504",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1469-1504",
      "markText": "上海地狭而近海，敌人陆海空联合作战，极易发挥威力，我军反攻因未能奏效。",
      "totalCount": 119,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23606318&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1469&rangeEnd=1504",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2e32e507168342ef2e3766?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1469&rangeEnd=1504"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23606318_3_1989-2018",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1989-2018",
      "markText": "我军因缺乏现代化武器，全赖血肉之躯与之相抗，所以伤亡甚重。",
      "totalCount": 119,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23606318&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1989&rangeEnd=2018",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2e32e507168342ef2e3766?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1989&rangeEnd=2018"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23606318_5_11353-11385",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "11353-11385",
      "markText": "十八日，我又接到暂停进攻的命令。这是开战以来，第三次的停攻命令。",
      "totalCount": 110,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23606318&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=11353&rangeEnd=11385",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2e32e507168342ef2e3766?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=11353&rangeEnd=11385"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23606318_9_8981-9173",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "8981-9173",
      "markText": "八月底，第九十八师转移阵地时，顾祝同命令留一个营固守宝山（我在侧听顾在电话上说的）。这个营长姚子青率全营官兵誓死抗击日军，宝山失陷，该营无一生存，真是可歌可泣。",
      "totalCount": 104,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23606318&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=8981&rangeEnd=9173",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2e32e507168342ef2e3766?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=8981&rangeEnd=9173"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23606318_5_9734-9921",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "9734-9921",
      "markText": "到日没时止，多有进展。突然又接到上级命令： 密。今晚不可进攻。另候后命（寒酉待参京电）。 于是攻击实施，又因此停止。",
      "totalCount": 96,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23606318&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=9734&rangeEnd=9921",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2e32e507168342ef2e3766?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=9734&rangeEnd=9921"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23606318_3_2700-2757",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2700-2757",
      "markText": "，后因敌人掌握制空权，行军不易，不能按照原定计划实施，复以命令下达仓促，部队准备不周，故原计划尚未实现便开始撤退。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23606318&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2700&rangeEnd=2757",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2e32e507168342ef2e3766?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2700&rangeEnd=2757"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23606318_6_14005-14070",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "14005-14070",
      "markText": "始终守住阵地，因此伤亡惨重。胡宗南一声不叫，顾祝同知道了，在电话中说今晚派某部来换防，胡才说再不换防，明天我也要拿枪上火线顶缺了。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23606318&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=14005&rangeEnd=14070",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2e32e507168342ef2e3766?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=14005&rangeEnd=14070"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23606318_6_15399-15495",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "15399-15495",
      "markText": "次日，敌人以坦克领头，向大场附近进攻，守该地的第十八师朱耀华部是湖南部队，兵力薄弱，正面过广，阵地被突破，朱耀华师长羞愤自杀，这是八一三抗战后上海方面第一个战死殉国的师长，应该受到人民的尊敬。",
      "totalCount": 84,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23606318&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=15399&rangeEnd=15495",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2e32e507168342ef2e3766?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=15399&rangeEnd=15495"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23606318_6_11013-11111",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "11013-11111",
      "markText": "由于罗店方面能顶住，而上海方面逐步撤退至江湾、大场，又未拿下虹口的敌军据点，张治中在电话中遭到蒋介石痛骂，他接受不了，将电话中断，不久被免去总司令职，后来为湖南省主席，从此再不带兵，只搞政治工作。",
      "totalCount": 80,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23606318&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=11013&rangeEnd=11111",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2e32e507168342ef2e3766?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=11013&rangeEnd=11111"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23606318_6_8818-8846",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "8818-8846",
      "markText": "他说：“不能这样欺骗领袖。”这一整天就毫无作为地过去了。",
      "totalCount": 78,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23606318&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=8818&rangeEnd=8846",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2e32e507168342ef2e3766?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=8818&rangeEnd=8846"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23606318_9_8641-8689",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "8641-8689",
      "markText": "顾每天早晚与蒋介石通电话，报告情况，由蒋在电话中指示某师调到哪里，某师如何作战，顾祝同作了传令兵",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23606318&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=8641&rangeEnd=8689",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2e32e507168342ef2e3766?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=8641&rangeEnd=8689"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23606318_54_4110-4161",
      "chapterUid": 54,
      "range": "4110-4161",
      "markText": "他翻身而起，抽出自卫双枪，左右开弓，当场击毙敌兵七名，然后用最后一颗子弹，射向自己的太阳穴，杀身成仁。",
      "totalCount": 70,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23606318&chapterUid=54&rangeStart=4110&rangeEnd=4161",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2e32e507168342ef2e3766?chapterUid=54&rangeStart=4110&rangeEnd=4161"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23606318_3_3019-3074",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "3019-3074",
      "markText": "2．日军官兵在战场上均能发挥奋斗牺牲，前仆后继，有武士道与大和魂之精神，彼虽为我之敌人，亦应取其所长而效法之。",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23606318&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3019&rangeEnd=3074",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2e32e507168342ef2e3766?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3019&rangeEnd=3074"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23606318_12_1167-1264",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "1167-1264",
      "markText": "在全军退却沪西前，我请第五二四团的团附谢晋元中校和该团第一营营长杨瑞符少校两位同志到“四行仓库”（大陆、金城、盐业、中南四银行联营的仓库）我的司令部里，我亲自交给他们“死守上海最后阵地”的命令。",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23606318&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1167&rangeEnd=1264",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2e32e507168342ef2e3766?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1167&rangeEnd=1264"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23606318_17_3502-3537",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "3502-3537",
      "markText": "在江湾防守战役中，最使我感动终生难忘的莫过于以上所说的这两件壮烈史实。",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23606318&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=3502&rangeEnd=3537",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2e32e507168342ef2e3766?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=3502&rangeEnd=3537"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23606318_30_5102-5195",
      "chapterUid": 30,
      "range": "5102-5195",
